data.description: Step into this well-maintained Wilmington Coastal patio ranch home. This home offers 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, with den/office and is loaded with many upgrades. Hardwood floors, crown molding, recessed lighting, and much more. The kitchen has granite countertops, gas range, island, pantry, and stainless-steel appliances. Large owner's suite has doorway to covered back porch. The ensuite has large shower with seating area and double vanities. The dining room is perfect for family gatherings with a stone two-sided gas fireplace that goes from dining room to living room. The den has French doors and is perfect as an office, den, or a relaxing sitting room. But when ready you can step out onto your front porch or back porch which are both covered and relax overlooking your maintenance-free yard. HOA maintains snow removal and landscaping for care-free living. The community offers a pool, playground, and walking paths.
